001package com.crossideas.ap.common.external.enums;
002
003/**
004 * The Enum RequestResponse. <li>{@link #AUTHORIZED}</li>
005 * 
006 * <li>{@link #REJECTED}</li>
007 * 
008 * <li>{@link #WAITING_ASYNCHRONOUS}</li>
009 * 
010 * <li>{@link #WAITING_SYNCHRONOUS}</li>
011 * 
012 */
013public enum RequestResponse {
014
015        /** The authorized. */
016        AUTHORIZED(1, "AUTHORIZED"),
017
018        /** The rejected. */
019        REJECTED(2, "REJECTED"),
020
021        /** The waiting asynchronous. */
022        WAITING_ASYNCHRONOUS(3, "WAITING_ASYNCHRONOUS"),
023
024        /** The waiting synchronous. */
025        WAITING_SYNCHRONOUS(4, "WAITING_SYNCHRONOUS"), ;
026
027        /** The code. */
028        private int code;
029
030        /** The value. */
031        private String value;
032
033        /**
034         * Instantiates a new request response.
035         *
036         * @param code
037         *            the code
038         * @param value
039         *            the value
040         */
041        private RequestResponse(int code, String value) {
042                this.code = code;
043                this.value = value;
044        }
045
046        /**
047         * Gets the value.
048         *
049         * @return the value
050         */
051        public String getValue() {
052                return value;
053        }
054
055        /**
056         * Sets the value.
057         *
058         * @param value
059         *            the new value
060         */
061        public void setValue(String value) {
062                this.value = value;
063        }
064
065        /**
066         * Gets the code.
067         *
068         * @return the code
069         */
070        public int getCode() {
071                return code;
072        }
073
074        /**
075         * Sets the code.
076         *
077         * @param code
078         *            the new code
079         */
080        public void setCode(int code) {
081                this.code = code;
082        }
083
084        /**
085         * Gets the.
086         *
087         * @param code
088         *            the code
089         * @return the request response
090         */
091        public static RequestResponse get(int code) {
092
093                RequestResponse[] list = RequestResponse.values();
094                for (int i = 0; i < list.length; i++) {
095                        if (code == (list[i].getCode())) {
096                                return list[i];
097                        }
098                }
099                return null;
100        }
101}
